<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Vim on Ehlxr's Blog</title><link>https://3w.vercel.app/tags/Vim/</link><description>Recent content in Vim on Ehlxr's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 02 Dec 2016 20:46:05 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://3w.vercel.app/tags/Vim/rss.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Vim Tab 设置为 4 个空格</title><link>https://3w.vercel.app/2016/12/02/Vim-Tab-%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BA-4-%E4%B8%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%A0%BC/</link><pubDate>Fri, 02 Dec 2016 20:46:05 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://3w.vercel.app/2016/12/02/Vim-Tab-%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%E4%B8%BA-4-%E4%B8%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%A0%BC/</guid><description>&lt;p>在 &lt;code>vim&lt;/code> 的配置文件中（Liunx：&lt;code>/etc/vimrc&lt;/code>）中添加以下代码后，重启 &lt;code>vim&lt;/code> 即可实现按 &lt;code>TAB&lt;/code> 产生 &lt;code>4&lt;/code> 个空格：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#f0f0f0;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#007020">set&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#bb60d5">ts&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#666">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#40a070">4&lt;/span> &lt;span style="color:#60a0b0;font-style:italic"># 注：ts 是 tabstop 的缩写，设 TAB 宽 4 个空格&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>&lt;span style="color:#007020">set&lt;/span> expandtab
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>对于已保存的文件，可以使用下面的方法进行空格和 &lt;code>TAB&lt;/code> 的替换：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>TAB&lt;/code> 替换为空格：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="background-color:#f0f0f0;-moz-tab-size:2;-o-tab-size:2;tab-size:2;">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>:set &lt;span style="color:#bb60d5">ts&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#666">=&lt;/span>&lt;span style="color:#40a070">4&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>:set expandtab
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>:%retab!
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item></channel></rss>